        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 3. Drosera quartzicola. A. Front view of the flower. B. Close-up of the front view of the flower, detail of the reproductive organs. C. Close-up of the flower bud, showing the dense indumentum of eglandular hairs and translucentyellow short-stalked globose (‘TSG’) trichomes. D. Close-up of the adaxial surface of the petiole, showing the large number of TSG trichomes. Photos by P. M. Gonella." ;
